  "title": "TCM Physician",
  "description": "<p>We are an established MOH licensed medical clinic of over 7 years looking to expand our services for acupuncture / TCM. <br />Currently we are looking for part-time initially to gain patients and subsequently converting to full-time. <br />We are located in the CBD area. <br /></p><p><strong>Requirements / Job Description</strong></p><p>The candidate should have diploma or degree and registration with TCM practioners board in Singapore <br />At least 2 years of experience<br />Are able to develop a variety of programs using their TCM skills <br />Has good communication skills and interpersonal skills to develop good rapport with patients <br />Not shy to be in marketing videos and able to give educational talks when required.<br /></p><p><strong>Part-Time Role</strong><br /><br /><strong>Salary:</strong> TBD</p><p><br /></p>",
